column5: What a SICK design job Ben Woo and Sheldon Hatch did on my new jersey!! The owner of the print shop even said it was the nicest design he's seen come through so far! I'm totally thrilled with it and cant wait to get the tourny season started!
mmmm, tile! j/k  sick jersey, I'd rock it hard
nice jamie !!! good luck this year bro !!! your new boat rocks man !!!!

Looks pretty, wheres your Tilley hat, I wouldnt trade it for my reliable faded camo T-shirt, with air conditioning holes, and my old track pants with the ass out of them, thats the clothin for catching big bad fish with teeth, and not those little stagnant greeners that hang around docks and stumps.
